    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，起源下面放两个子节点：一个是'悠久的历史'，这个我想用书本来表示，比较直观；另一个是'普及化'，重点提一下英国的托尼·博赞，他是 popular psychology 领域的作者。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Long history",
        "::icon(fa fa-book)",
        "Popularisation",
        "British popular psychology author Tony Buzan"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在Origins下面加了Long history并配了fa-book图标，Popularisation下面挂了Tony Buzan的信息。现在来弄Research分支，您刚才说的研究现状具体包含哪些？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Research",
        "On effectiveness<br/and features",
        "On Automatic creation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Research分两块：一是关于思维导图的效果和特性研究，这个标题可能有点长需要换行；二是自动生成方面的研究，下面再细分几个应用场景，比如创造性技术、战略规划、论证映射这些。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "On effectiveness<br/and features",
        "On Automatic creation",
        "Uses",
        "Creative techniques",
        "Strategic planning",
        "Argument mapping"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
